Currently if you have browse users permission, you will be able to search for users from all groups in the user picker. If you view a particular users profile, and they are in some groups you are not a member of, the groups you are not a member of will not be shown. 

If you have browse users global permission we might as well show all groups in the user profile since you can find out the other groups by way of the user picker anyway.

