For a WAR deployment, our [install docs|http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA/Installing+JIRA+on+Tomcat+6.0#InstallingJIRAonTomcat6.0-4.UpdateTomcatLibraries] link to jira-jars-tomcat6.zip, containing jars to add to Tomcat. This includes log4j-1.2.7.jar.  In JIRA 4.0 this version is so old as to be incompatible with slf4j, which then prints (to stderr and stdout):

{noformat}
SLF4J: This version of SLF4J requires log4j version 1.2.12 or later. See also http://www.slf4j.org/codes.html#log4j_version
{noformat}

